Class LoggedOnCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.thomasc.steamkit.steam3.steamclient.callbackmgr.CallbackMsg
      • uk.co.thomasc.steamkit.steam3.handlers.steamuser.callbacks.LoggedOnCallback

  • public final class LoggedOnCallback
extends CallbackMsg
    This callback is returned in response to an attempt to log on to the Steam3 network through SteamUser.
